<div class="container-fluid welcomePageContainer">
  <div class="hero">
    <!-- <img src="images/splash_filtered.jpg" alt="This is an image of two women laughing with each other at an outdoor cafe."> -->
    <p>
      Studies show that mentors and friends determine your career path. Find that support group here:
    </p>
    <div id="joinNowCTA">
      <%= link_to "Join Now", default_omniauth_authorize_path %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="unit">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 class='sectionHead light'>
          How Joining Can Help
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
        <div class="thumbnail dark">
          <%= image_tag "icons/find_peers.png", alt: "An image of three clipart heads." %>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>Find Peers</h3>
            <p>
              Talk to other women who are as dedicated to their careers as you are. We employ our proven algorithmic
              process to create "mini-meetup" groups of three that are selected by peer groups, industry, and city.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
        <div class="thumbnail dark">
          <%= image_tag "icons/find_mentorship.png", alt: "An image of a clipart head in a magnifying glass." %>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>Find Mentorship</h3>
            <p>
              Connect to intelligent women via Skype to either seek advice and insight on your personal career path, or
              role playing feedback on other work related situations. Our mentorship program allows you to meet with as
              many new mentors in order to establish that mentor relationship that you desire.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
        <div class="thumbnail dark">
          <%= image_tag "icons/mentor_others.png", alt: "An image of two clipart heads." %>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>Mentor Others</h3>
            <p>
              You don't have to be a top executive at a Fortune 100 company, all you need is the experience to provide
              your mentee with beneficial guidance. Connect with other women interested in your position, and help other
              women attain the same career success as you. This program is not a full time committment; you are able to
              chat with your mentee when it is convenient for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

