              Continue meeting intelligent and influential women at least once a month for career advice or for
              developing new friendships!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrows">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <%= image_tag "icons/arrow.png" %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
